title: Marisa C. Peczuh
text: Welcome to my website! Click around to learn more about me.

title: About
text:
I’m a PhD student at the University of Minnesota, Twin Cities in the Psychological Foundations of Education program. I am interested in supporting students’ identities in learning environments and contributing to educational equity through research and practice.
I grew up in small town in Connecticut, attended college in New York, and lived in Rhode Island before moving to Minnesota. Outside of school and work, I also enjoy playing and watching women’s basketball, exploring the outdoors, eating at sweet treats, doing arts and crafts, and traveling!
